<h2 id="requirements">Requirements</h2>

<p>Well, the requirements are quite simple. We will be needing the following,</p>

<ul>
  <li>Xcode 11.4 beta or above.</li>
  <li>Bundle identifier of your app.</li>
  <li>The device identifier of your currently active simulator.</li>
  <li>Push notification payload.</li>
  <li>Terminal.</li>
</ul>
<div>
    <a class="notification sponsor" href="https://winya.link/get" target="_blank">
